WEBVTT

00:00:01.753 --> 00:00:02.920
A few weeks ago,

00:00:02.944 --> 00:00:07.659
somebody tweeted during the midterm
elections in the United States

00:00:07.683 --> 00:00:10.602
that Election Day
should be made a holiday.

00:00:10.626 --> 00:00:12.178
And I retweeted, saying,

00:00:12.202 --> 00:00:14.798
"Well, you're welcome to come
to my country and vote.

00:00:14.822 --> 00:00:18.160
You'll get the whole week off
to allow the military to count it."

00:00:18.742 --> 00:00:20.211
I come from Togo, by the way.

00:00:20.235 --> 00:00:23.507
It is a beautiful country
located in West Africa.

00:00:23.531 --> 00:00:27.063
There are some cool,
interesting facts about my country.

00:00:27.446 --> 00:00:30.610
Togo has been ruled
by the same family for 51 years,